property.code: {{velocity}} ## Include the three.js utils #if ($xcontext.action != 'edit') ## Import jsx and ssx #set ($discard = $xwiki.jsx.use('Macros.ThreeMacro.Code.ThreeUtils')) #set ($discard = $xwiki.ssx.use('Macros.ThreeMacro.Code.ThreeUtils')) ## Get width and height #set ($width = $wikimacro.parameters.width) #set ($height = $wikimacro.parameters.height) ## Add "px" if the width or height are plain numbers #if ($numbertool.toNumber($width).toString().equals($width)) #set ($width = "${width}px") #end #if ($numbertool.toNumber($height).toString().equals($height)) #set ($height = "${height}px") #end #set ($fileURLs = []) ## Get URL of the attachments and put them into the main array #if ($wikimacro.parameters.attachmentRef) #foreach ($attachment in $wikimacro.parameters.attachmentRef) #set ($attachmentURL = $xwiki.getURL($attachment)) #set ($discard = $fileURLs.add($attachmentURL)) #end #end ## Put the file URLs into the main array #if ($wikimacro.parameters.ref) #foreach ($fileURL in $wikimacro.parameters.ref) #set ($discard = $fileURLs.add($fileURL)) #end #end #set ($canvasId = $util.generateRandomString(5)) (% id="threeCanvas${canvasId}" class="macro-three-container" style="width: ${width}; height: ${height}" data-files='${jsontool.serialize(${fileURLs})}' data-type="$!wikimacro.parameters.type" data-zoom-out="$!wikimacro.parameters.defaultZoomOut" data-background="$!wikimacro.parameters.background" data-disable-controls="$!wikimacro.parameters.disableControls" data-auto-rotate="$!wikimacro.parameters.autoRotate" data-auto-rotate-speed="$!wikimacro.parameters.autoRotateSpeed" %)((($!wikimacro.content))) #end {{/velocity}}
